1613408701-who-s-next-to-get-canceled-on.description:
Larry rocks!

The "Cancel culture" is fascism.

The web moguls, like Google, Fascebook, and Shitter, are disgrace to the internet. What they do is the most anti-internet crime ever. The BigTech Censorship goes against every norm and principle of the behaviour on the internet.

And they are an ungrateful disgrace. They made their fortunes only thanks to the US. Nowhere else in the world they would have such conditions to make something so big "out of a garage". Sergey Brin had to have his parents move him out of the USSR before he could make anything like Google. Jan Koum had to move out of Ukraine before he could make WhatsApp.

The freedom of the internet is the free spirit of the US.

Just imagine what kind of an internet we had if it came from China (firewalls everywhere) or Europe (bureaucratic and fractured)!

The style of the internet is the style of Alan Key, not of Dijkstra. And Alan Key came out of a US Airforce project! He got the idea of the object from some "unknown sergeant", as he says himself in "The short history of Smalltalk".

The totalitarian social-fascism has already ruined "the Silicon Valley" of 20s century, Detroit. Now it is destroying California, and no one of these moguls does anything about it. They used everything the Valley offered and now they abuse it.

They either cowardly cave to the woke mob or do these crimes from their own conscience. Either way, they endanger everybody. Information and disinformation are powerful things in human society.

And screw Apple too!

1613410741-The Truth About PCR Tests.mp4.title: The Truth About PCR Tests, Dr. Sam Bailey (720p)
1613410741-The Truth About PCR Tests.mp4.description:
It is a repost from her LBRY/Odysee channel. 

She explains clearly and in detail the downsides of using this test as a serious proof of infection. For example, one of them is the fact that the detects *part* of the virus genome, i.e. separate genes, not the full genome, and not the full virus itself. Therefore, if your immune system encountered the virus and tore it into pieces, then you can still get this test "positive".

In fact, some weeks ago the President of Portugal got both positive and negative result of the test made at the same time. And the Portuguese football star Cristiano Ronaldo got "positive" result three times in a row, when obviously he would have collapsed on the football field if he were infected to any noticeable level.

I myself had to deal with this, because I had to travel in order to sort out issues with documents. The results to my "negative" tests included a page with the doctor's opinion, that basically said that the test alone does not mean anything and you need to do a full and proper clinical examination, with the attention to symptoms and blood tests.

I think everybody must know that this test is not a proof for the coronavirus infections, and that it can be false positive or false negative.

It is a disgrace how the officials, medics and international bureaucrats impose this stuff on us with all possible strictness and hide or just lie about what this thing is.

1613504533-Rothbardians vs. Free Bankers.title: No Boom-Bust Systems: Rothbardians vs. “Free Bankers” on Fractional Reserve Banking Robert P. Murphy
1613504533-Rothbardians vs. Free Bankers.description:
Boom-bust cycle is natural to the fractional reserve banking systems. An Austrian economist Robert P. Murphy explains in detail the difference between two views at this problem in the Austrian (capitalist) system. And he clarifies how the the problem comes about along the way.

Whether it is a central bank or many private ones, they do credit expansion, which creates the fake financial boom that is not supported by any real economic performance. It is bound to go bust. As the housing market went bust in 2008, after the artificial boom of "affordable housing" that was created by politicians on demand from the voters.

When you have many free banks, they are not synchronised, their actions are not coherent. Therefore the booms and busts are smaller. As it was in the 19th century Canada, presented in this lecture.

I copied the lecture from [Mises Media YouTube channel](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U69Qrz0xtbI). All credit goes to them and Mr. Murphy.

Murphy refers to another lecture on the same conference: "The Austrian Theory of the Business Cycle" by Roger W. Garrison. I uploaded that lecture too.

The video description on YouTube:

Recorded at the Mises Institute in Auburn, Alabama, on July 17, 2018.

Mises University is the world's leading instructional program in the Austrian School of economics, and is the essential training ground for economists who are looking beyond the mainstream.

Licence: Creative Commons Attribution licence (reuse allowed)

Один – их, а другой привозят американцы на самолете"
* Понимал ли я, когда пришел в правительство, что нужно сделать, чтобы экономика Грузии заработала? Конечно! Это несложно. Это настолько просто, что люди не верят, что в этом и есть ответ: нужно дать волю. Свободные люди всегда найдут самое лучшее решение
